						<description>Caliber: 40x46mm. 1-round tube. Single shot.					
The X1 is an experimental 40mm grenade launcher designed by Springfield Armory, designed to give the capability of underbarrel launchers to the M14 as was being tested with AR-15-type rifles with Colt's XM148. The X1 was ultimately not very successful and never put into service, but remains a unique part of the M14's history.</description>
